reviews.text: $10/ oyster, who can resist and say no? We ended up having 7 dozens. For $10, the quality is really good! It’s so fresh, sweet and so rich of flavours! Other dishes are good too! Like their services, polite and attentive, will go back again

The shop provides different kinds of oysters in the world for you to choose to taste. Especially, it provides the lowest price of oyster($10.00 per piece)for you to taste. The service is very good as you may get much more information from the manger. It's worth to have a luncheon or dinner there.

It's a good choice when you would like to have something a little high class when in Tai Kok Tsui.

result.name: 萬發海鮮火鍋菜館

reviews.text: 班夥計都夠膽死，個餐牌大大隻字寫住炒底加十蚊，落單嗰陣死都要話加20，跟住攞返張餐牌督住隻字畀佢自己睇，先死死地氣改返十蚊，好喇啲野食上到嚟，係我知我食午市飯
地方偏避，交通不便，泊車困難，食物味道一般，價錢不便宜，幸而伙記服務還可
乳豬，薯仔牛柳粒，啫啫芥蘭都不錯，其他我覺得一般吧！份量夠大，人多來吃的話不點海鮮，人均兩百多也很合理。
菜色豐富 火喉夠 招牌豬肚雞煲 非常好味 服務 ok
埋單果位阿姐服務員態度非常差勁，不會再去光顧。
